title: In the other case, find the two closest sites such that one partner works at one and the other works at the other. Call these two sites H and L -- H being the site assigned to the the worker with the higher burden, and L the other one.
pid: 2ed7d40d-0f1c-4c73-9a5f-56d90a320420
body: |2-
  Consider what would happen if instead they shared H. Now this reduces to the first case -- find the optimal way to split H between them.
